column5: Don't know if this is just a sick coincidence or if I'm getting  paranoid, but .... 2007 - Chinese year of the Chicken - Bird Flu Pandemic devastates parts of Asia 2008 - Chinese year of the Horse - Equine Influenza decimates Australian racing 2009 - Chinese year of the Pig - Swine Flu Pandemic kills hundreds of pigs/humans around the globe.  It gets worse........Next year......2010 - Chinese year of the noodle - what could possibly go wrong? HH
[ Chinese year of the noodle - what could possibly go wrong? HH    Use it or lose it!

No need to worry...You've got your zodiacs all mixed up.  2005 was the year of the chicken, 2008 was the year of the rat and 2009 is the year of the Ox...No noodle sign to speak of...With that said, 2013 might not be the year for your snakes
